Actuarial Pricing of Heart Disease Insurance in Malaysia Using CODA–ARIMA and Lee–Carter Mortality Models

Final Year Project

  • Backtested and validated models using AIC, BIC, RMSE, MAE, and MAPE, ensuring accuracy and reliability of pricing assumptions.
